readme:
# [`node-llama-cpp`](https://github.com/withcatai/node-llama-cpp)
This is a prebuilt binary package for [`node-llama-cpp`](https://github.com/withcatai/node-llama-cpp) for macOS arm64 with Metal support.

Do not install this package directly.
